data.description: After many years, and many memories made, the sellers of this lovely 2-story home within the highly coveted neighborhood of Yankee Trace are ready to say good-bye. The sellers have loved the neighborhood and all of the amenities that are offered included, but not limited, the award-winning golf course, multiple maintained walking paths, community pools, clubhouse, and tennis courts. The main floor flows seamlessly into each room with the circular floor plan and offers a bedroom with a full bath. The primary bedroom on the second floor features a large ensuite bathroom and dual closets for ample storage space. Three more spacious bedrooms and a full bath complete the second floor. The lower level is ready to become your own personal oasis. The possibilities are endless! Whether you are a home gym aficionado or want to create the perfect movie and game room, the space is yours for the making. The home is ready for you to come in and make it your own.
